'''Project Ara'''是[[Google先進科技與計畫部門|Google先進科技與計畫部門]]的一項專案，目的是希望透過[[開源硬件|開源硬件]]開發一款可高度[[模組|模組化]]的[[智慧型手機|智慧型手機]]。該專案允許[[消費者|消費者]]自由選擇與替換甚至移除任何的零組件，包括[[處理器|處理器]]、[[螢幕|螢幕]]、[[鍵盤|鍵盤]]、[[電池|電池]]及其他等等手機常見的零組件，這使得消費者可以輕鬆替換掉單一的一個故障致或過時的零組件，從而減少[[電子垃圾|電子垃圾]]，並且延長手機的[[產品生命週期|產品生命週期]]<ref>{{cite web|last=Byford|first=Sam|title=Motorola reveals ambitious plan to build modular smartphones|url=http://www.theverge.com/2013/10/29/5041336/motorola-project-ara-modular-smartphones|work=The Verge|publisher=Vox Media|accessdate=2013-10-29|date=2013-10-29|archive-date=2013-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029231533/http://www.theverge.com/2013/10/29/5041336/motorola-project-ara-modular-smartphones|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Musil|first=Steven|title=Motorola unveils Project Ara for custom smartphones|url=http://news.cnet.com/8301-1035_3-57609735-94/motorola-unveils-project-ara-for-custom-smartphones/|work=CNET|publisher=CBS Interactive|accessdate=2013-10-29|date=2013-10-29|archive-date=2013-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029210159/http://news.cnet.com/8301-1035_3-57609735-94/motorola-unveils-project-ara-for-custom-smartphones/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

Project Ara原先由[[Motorola|Motorola]]旗下的先進科技與計畫部門負責。雖然Google將Motorola出售給[[聯想集團|聯想集團]]，但該部門仍屬於Google旗下，是Google專案之一。

2016年9月1日[[路透社|路透社]]根據Google內部人士消息報導，Google已停止Project Ara開發計畫<ref>{{cite web|last=Love|first=Julia|title=Exclusive: Google shelves plan for phone with interchangeable parts - sources|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-google-smartphone-idUSKCN11806C|work=Reuters|publisher=Reuters|accessdate=2016-09-03|date=2016-09-01|archive-date=2016-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160902200911/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-google-smartphone-idUSKCN11806C|dead-url=no}}</ref>；該消息在同月2日被Google發言人向科技新聞網站VentureBeat證實。<ref>{{cite web|last=Weber|first=Harrison|title=Google confirms suspension of Ara modular smartphone project|url=http://venturebeat.com/2016/09/02/google-confirms-it-has-suspended-its-ara-modular-smartphone-project/|work=VentureBeat|publisher=VentureBeat|accessdate=2016-09-03|date=2016-09-02|archive-date=2016-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160909143635/http://venturebeat.com/2016/09/02/google-confirms-it-has-suspended-its-ara-modular-smartphone-project/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==框架與模組==
Google計畫透過[[Google_Play|Google Play]]來販賣模組，另外保持第三方模組的支援，但是所有的第三方模組都需要通過Google的認證<ref name="ap">{{cite web|last=Summerson|first=Cameron|title=Fascinating: Project Ara Team Member Gives Us The First Glimpse Of How The Product Will Work In Model Demo At LAUNCH|url=http://www.androidpolice.com/2014/02/28/fascinating-project-ara-team-member-gives-us-the-first-glimpse-of-how-the-product-will-work-in-model-demo-at-launch/|work=Android Police|accessdate=2014-03-04|archive-date=2014-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140304053805/http://www.androidpolice.com/2014/02/28/fascinating-project-ara-team-member-gives-us-the-first-glimpse-of-how-the-product-will-work-in-model-demo-at-launch/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="pha">{{cite web|last=Kennemer|first=Quentyn|title=Project Ara presented on video at LAUNCH conference; new details revealed|url=http://www.androidpolice.com/2014/02/28/fascinating-project-ara-team-member-gives-us-the-first-glimpse-of-how-the-product-will-work-in-model-demo-at-launch/|work=Phandroid|accessdate=2014-03-04|archive-date=2014-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140308004417/http://www.androidpolice.com/2014/02/28/fascinating-project-ara-team-member-gives-us-the-first-glimpse-of-how-the-product-will-work-in-model-demo-at-launch/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Ara的原形機種有3種框架尺寸可供選擇：迷你、標準與平板電腦，各模組可相容於不同的主板之間，<ref name="ap" />且並不限制特定模組的安裝上限。<ref name="pha" />

Ara透過安裝各種模組可以提供一般智慧型手機的各式功能，也可透過安裝專業級模組提供更專業化的功能，包含但不限於遊戲控制器、投影設備等。同時Ara支援模組的[[熱插拔|熱插拔]]，若安裝一個以上的電池模組，即可在可維持一定續航力的前提下進行熱插拔<ref name="ehc">{{Cite web |url=http://chinese.engadget.com/2014/04/10/project-ara-mdk/ |title=徹底顛覆手機市場「星象」？Google模組化手機MDK文件揭露更多Porject Ara計劃細節 |accessdate=2014-04-10 |archive-date=2014-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140412010555/http://chinese.engadget.com/2014/04/10/project-ara-mdk/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。模組使用[[電永磁|電永磁]]固定於框架上。

